external_knowledge:
- 'Most recent discussions' refer to topics that are currently active in the database;
- The entity 'Marijuana' is the main subject of the articles;
- Emotional reactions refer to the sentiment scores calculated for each article.

- Beacon lights: Metaphor for significant or important news articles; 
- Torchbearers: Metaphor for authors who disseminate knowledge or news;
- Breakthroughs: Metaphor for articles classified as breaking news;
- Illuminated: Metaphor for the publication of articles bringing new information to light;
- Realms: Metaphor for topics, the areas or categories of information the articles cover;
- Cast shadows: Metaphor for the main entities around which the articles revolve or focus.

sql:
SELECT articles.title, topics.topic_name
FROM articles
JOIN topics ON articles.topic_id = topics.topic_id;
